title: Episode 54: Jade and the Indian Giver
itunes:title: Episode 54: Jade and the Indian Giver
description:
Jade Catta-Preta is our princess for the evening.

Bobby is the butler.

Khalyla is the orchestrator.

Gilbert is the gardener.

We talk foot AIDS, comedians in ballgowns, and Mongo The Destroyer.

 

Recorded August 15, 2016

Music by Bobby Lee

Instagram: @tigerbelly

Twitter: @thetigerbelly
